{"type": "article", "id": 4488, "title": "Objects 系列办公用品组合", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-18T07:41:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233602HPI1DARZMFtUkEny.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\tBase 是由 Mark Kelley 和 Richard Liu 两位设计师在旧金山开设的一家创意设计工作室。日前，两人推出了品牌最新的「Objects」系列办公用品组合，「001」, 「002」和「003」，采用了产自越南的宝丽石制作而成。其中，Objects 「001」与「002」是两个高度与大小皆不同的杯筒，而 Objects「003」是一个托盘与小杯子的组合，可以放在办公桌面收纳各种杂物，提供黑、白、灰与橙色 4 种选择，定价 30－36 美元不等，<a href=\"http://base-object.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233600zXITQyM5OtaDdcAR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233600vLjSaruny8Ep0459.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233601r3WqnP5ZxKdshzct.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233601viOw3SjdTR1NQDts.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233602rHN5f9cE12GRYiBF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}